s://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/servarica-com-2015-02-27-13-52-59-1024x597.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/servarica-com-2015-02-27-13-52-59.png.webp 1169w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/servarica-com-2015-02-27-13-52-59-300x175.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/servarica-com-2015-02-27-13-52-59-1024x597.png.webp 1024w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/servarica-com-2015-02-27-13-52-59.png.webp 1169w\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a>Hani, from <a href=\"https://servarica.com/\">Servarica</a>, is back after a few years with another exclusive offer for Low End Box with a high storage 3GB VPS 3 TB storage space offer. We really love that this exclusive package has 3 TB of disk space and 100 mbps unlimited bandwidth. A great option for people looking to backup files or run a media server. Servarica has been featured on Low End Box <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/?s=servarica&amp;searchsubmit=Find\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">five prior times</a> from 2011 to 2017, and now again for a sixth time in 2020. We consider them a \u201cResident Host\u201d because of their reliability and long term stability.</p><p>Servarica is a registered company in the province of Quebec (NEQ #1173530495). Their terms of service is available <a href=\"https://servarica.com/terms-of-service/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">on their website</a> for review. They accept PayPal, Alipay, Credit Cards and Crypto for payment.</p><p><strong>In their own words:</strong></p><div><em>\u201cservaRICA is VPS hosting provider in Canada that started in 2010, servaRICA is Tier 1 provider (we own all the hardware and manage the network and have IPs from ARIN directly). We are currently located in Montreal. </em><em>We have been in the business for many years, you can check our reviews here in LEB or LET from our old offers. </em><em>Our team will be ready to help you in case you have any issue just contact us through livechat in our site or through our ticketing system. </em><em>Please don\u2019t forget to review us so the others know about the service\u201d</em></div><p><strong>Their big storage VPS offer:&nbsp;</strong></p><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>3GB Xen</strong><p></p><ul><li>3GB RAM</li><li>3 CPU Cores</li><li>3 TB Disk Space</li><li>Unlimited 100mbps Bandwidth</li><li>1 x IPv4</li><li>/64 IPv6 on request</li><li>Xen</li><li>$10/month</li><li><a href=\"https://servarica.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=444\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>As always, feel free to share your experiences as well!</p><p>More information is available by reading more.</p><p><span id=\"more-21891\"></span></p><p>Orders coming from a proxy or VPN IP will not be accepted and neither will offers with an invalid address not matching the geolocation of the IP. There\u2019s a 7-day no-answer-required refund policy; Servarica will always ask why you cancel (as do most hosts). IPv6 is available on request.</p><p>More in their own words:</p><ul><li>Owned hardware.</li><li>Managing our network</li><li>Cheapest offer in the market based on specs</li><li>Unlimited BW 100mbps port with each offer</li><li>Track record of having one of the best customer service in LEB</li><li>Real 24/7 livechat and ticket support</li><li>We offer 7 days full refund with no question asked</li></ul><p>Servarica is a registered company in Quebec, Canada and has been for four years. The offer a monthly 99.9% uptime SLA, with the following compensation structure:</p><ul><li>99.9%: no refund</li><li>99.0% or more: 15% refund</li><li>97.0% or more: 30% refund</li><li>95.0% or more: 50% refund</li><li>Less than 95%: 100% refund</li></ul><p><strong>Network information</strong></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Cologix \u2013 Montreal, Canada</span><br>\nTest IPv4: <span class=\"original\">162.250.190.17&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong>Node Configurations:</strong></p><ul><li>The offers will go on nodes that run 2X 2650v2 or better</li><li>Each node have 128GB or more</li><li>Each node have 10gb uplink</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fservarica-10-month-3gb-vps-with-3-tb-disk-space-in-montreal-canada%2F&amp;t=Servarica%20-%20%2410%2Fmonth%203GB%20Xen%20VPS%20with%203%20TB%20disk%20space%20in%20Montreal%2C%20Canada\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Servarica%20-%20%2410%2Fmonth%203GB%20Xen%20VPS%20with%203%20TB%20disk%20space%20in%20Montreal%2C%20Canada&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fservarica-10-month-3gb-vps-with-3-tb-disk-space-in-montreal-canada%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fservarica-10-month-3gb-vps-with-3-tb-disk-space-in-montreal-canada%2F&amp;title=Servarica%20-%20%2410%2Fmonth%203GB%20Xen%20VPS%20with%203%20TB%20disk